  "decomposition_rationale": "The parent OrderSystem handles three distinct commands. ParseAndValidateInput handles input validation and routing logic (parent decides which child to call based on command). PlaceOrder, CancelOrder, and TrackOrder each handle a specific command workflow, ensuring separation of concerns and no cross-calls between siblings.",
